compilation :
pdflatex -jobname main-figure main





entete :



\documentclass[12pt] {article}
\usepackage[T1]{fontenc}
\usepackage[x11names, rgb]{xcolor}
\usepackage{tikz}
\usetikzlibrary{automata,arrows,er,external,fit,positioning,snakes,shapes,trees}
\usetikzlibrary{external}

\tikzexternalize{main}


\begin{document}

\begin{tikzpicture}


\end{tikzpicture}

\end{document} 




Pour inclure un fichier sans utiliser les packages pgf

    
    \beginpgfgraphicnamed{figure_0}
    \endpgfgraphicnamed
